sentence: Among the underlying components of the Russell 3000 index, we saw noteworthy options trading volume today in Barnes & Noble Inc (Symbol: BKS), where a total of 2,481 contracts have traded so far, representing approximately 248,100 underlying shares.
That amounts to about 41.8% of BKS's average daily trading volume over the past month of 593,245 shares.
Particularly high volume was seen for the $11 strike call option expiring July 15, 2016 , with 2,294 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 229,400 underlying shares of BKS.
